#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-sparc-disk.xml:501
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# <i>mkfs.ext2 /dev/sda1</i>\n"
"# <i>mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda4</i>\n"
